<div class="space-y-10">
  <div>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-5">The Mayor and City Council serve as the elected governing body of the City of Aberdeen. Together they are responsible for setting City policy, approving the annual budget, passing ordinances, and representing the interests of all Aberdeen residents.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The City Council holds regular public meetings where residents are encouraged to attend and participate. All meetings are open to the public.</p>
  </div>

